		description: "Turn more of your " + neighborhoodName + " website visitors into leads, calls, and sales.",
		icon: "⚡",
	},
];

// ── Top 3 featured services for "Popular Services" section ────────────────────
const featuredServices = [
	{
		slug: "seo",
		title: "Local SEO",
		description: `Get your ${neighborhoodName} business ranking at the top of Google for the searches that matter. We build comprehensive local SEO strategies — Google Business Profile optimization, citation building, on-page SEO, and neighborhood-specific content — that deliver consistent organic growth.`,
	},
	{
		slug: "paid-advertising",
		title: "Paid Advertising",
		description: `Launch precision-targeted Google and Meta ad campaigns that put your ${neighborhoodName} business in front of ready-to-buy customers. From keyword strategy to creative to conversion tracking, we manage everything and optimize for real revenue, not just clicks.`,
	},
	{
		slug: "web-design",
		title: "Web Design & CRO",
		description: `Your website is your 24/7 salesperson. We build fast, modern, conversion-optimized sites tailored to the ${neighborhoodName} market — designed to turn visitors into leads and calls from the moment they land.`,
	},
];

// ── Unique business reasons derived from character ────────────────────────────
const uniquePoints = [
	`${neighborhoodName} customers are research-driven — they compare options online before making any purchase decision. Businesses with strong digital presence win the sale before any in-person interaction.`,
	`Competition in ${neighborhoodName} is intensifying. Established businesses and new entrants are both investing in SEO and paid media. Without a strategy, you're handing customers to competitors.`,
	`The ${neighborhoodName} market rewards local authenticity. Marketing that reflects the neighborhood's culture and values resonates far more than generic campaigns built for a national audience.`,
	`Mobile search dominates locally. The majority of ${neighborhoodName} residents find businesses on their phones — often within hours of making a purchase. Being visible and optimized for mobile is non-negotiable.`,
];

const whyPoints = [
	`We understand ${neighborhoodName}'s competitive landscape — who your real competitors are, what's working, and where the gaps are.`,
	`Our strategies are tailored to the ${neighborhoodName} customer profile, not recycled from a template built for another market.`,
	`You get measurable results with clear reporting — no jargon, no vanity metrics.`,
	`We're a Chicago team. We know the city's neighborhoods, culture, and business environment better than any remote agency.`,
];

// ── Related blog posts (static fallback — 3 relevant posts) ──────────────────
const relatedPosts = [
	{
		href: "/blog/local-seo-chicago-businesses/",
		title: "The Complete Local SEO Guide for Chicago Small Businesses",
		excerpt: "How to dominate local search, optimize your Google Business Profile, and build citations that drive real foot traffic.",
	},
	{
		href: "/blog/google-ads-chicago/",
		title: "How Chicago Businesses Can Get More From Google Ads",
		excerpt: "A practical breakdown of campaign structure, bidding strategies, and neighborhood-level targeting that reduces wasted spend.",
	},
	{
		href: "/blog/website-conversion-optimization/",
		title: "Why Your Chicago Business Website Isn't Converting (And How to Fix It)",
		excerpt: "The most common conversion killers on local business websites — and the specific fixes that produce measurable results.",
	},
];

const pageTitle = `Digital Marketing in ${neighborhoodName}, Chicago | The Chicago Marketing Agency`;
const pageDesc = `Full-service digital marketing for ${neighborhoodName} businesses. SEO, web design, paid advertising, social media, and more — tailored to your neighborhood.`;

const baseUrl = "https://thechicagomarketingagency.com";
---

<Base title={pageTitle} description={pageDesc}>
	<!-- ── JSON-LD: LocalBusiness ── -->
	<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
		"@context": "https://schema.org",
		"@type": "MarketingAgency",
		"name": "The Chicago Marketing Agency",
		"url": baseUrl,
		"description": pageDesc,
		"areaServed": {
			"@type": "Place",
			"name": `${neighborhoodName}, Chicago, IL`
		},
		"address": {
			"@type": "PostalAddress",
			"addressLocality": "Chicago",
			"addressRegion": "IL",
			"addressCountry": "US"
		}
	})} />
	<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
		"@context": "https://schema.org",
		"@type": "BreadcrumbList",
		"itemListElement": [
			{ "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": `${baseUrl}/` },
			{ "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": neighborhoodName, "item": `${baseUrl}/${neighborhood}/` }
		]
	})} />

	<!-- ── HERO (split layout: text left / image right) ── -->
	<section class="sa-hero">
		<div class="container sa-hero-inner">
			<!-- Left: text content -->
			<div class="sa-hero-content">
				<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
					<a href="/">Home</a>
					<span>/</span>
					<span>{neighborhoodName}</span>
				</nav>
				<span class="eyebrow">{neighborhoodName}, Chicago</span>
				<h1>Digital Marketing Services in {neighborhoodName}, Chicago</h1>
				<p class="sa-hero-desc">
					{neighborhoodName} is {neighborhoodCharacter}. We build data-driven marketing strategies that match that reality and deliver measurable results for local businesses.
				</p>
				<div class="sa-hero-actions">
					<a href="/free-seo-audit/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Marketing Audit →</a>
					<a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline-white">Talk to Our Team</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Right: neighborhood image -->
			<div class="sa-hero-visual">
				<img
					src={heroImageUrl}
					alt={`${neighborhoodName} neighborhood, Chicago`}
					width="800"
					height="560"
					loading="eager"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── SERVICES GRID ── -->
	<section class="sa-services">
		<div class="container">
			<p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--red); display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center;">What We Offer</p>
			<h2 class="sa-services-heading">Marketing Services for {neighborhoodName} Businesses</h2>
			<p class="sa-services-sub">Every service is tailored to the unique dynamics of the {neighborhoodName} market.</p>
			<div class="sa-grid">
				{services.map((svc) => (
					<a href={`/${neighborhood}/${svc.slug}/`} class="sa-card">
						<span class="sa-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">{svc.icon}</span>
						<h3 class="sa-card-title">{svc.title}</h3>
						<p class="sa-card-desc">{svc.description}</p>
						<span class="sa-card-link">Learn more →</span>
					</a>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── ABOUT THE NEIGHBORHOOD ── -->
	<section class="sa-about">
		<div class="container sa-about-inner">
			<div class="sa-about-text">
				<span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--red); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">About the Area</span>
				<h2>About {neighborhoodName}</h2>
				<p>
					{neighborhoodName} is {neighborhoodCharacter}. For businesses operating in this market, the difference between growth and stagnation often comes down to digital visibility — who shows up first in search, who runs the most effective ads, and whose website actually converts visitors into customers.
				</p>
				<p>
					We've worked with businesses across all of Chicago's neighborhoods and understand that {neighborhoodName} has its own dynamics. The customer profile is distinct. The competitive density varies by category. The way residents and visitors discover businesses in {neighborhoodName} is shaped by the neighborhood's culture, demographic makeup, and the digital habits of the people who live and spend money there.
				</p>
				<p>
					That's why we don't apply a one-size-fits-all approach. Every strategy we build for a {neighborhoodName} business starts with a thorough audit of the local competitive landscape, an analysis of existing digital presence, and a clear picture of where the biggest opportunities are — before we ever recommend a single tactic.
				</p>
				<p>
					Chicago is a city of neighborhoods, and the best marketing reflects that. Whether you're a restaurant, a law firm, a retail shop, or a service business, we build strategies that are specifically calibrated for {neighborhoodName} — not copied from a playbook built for a different market.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── WHAT MAKES THIS NEIGHBORHOOD UNIQUE ── -->
	<section class="sa-unique">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--red); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">Market Dynamics</span>
